<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038399" n="143v"/>
<p><!-- ToDo: In einem Vorspann darauf hinweisen, dass in der Handschrift der Brief mitten in der Seite des Entwurfheftes beginnt. -->
   <lb/>Gratias Tibi ago maximas, tum quia <rs type="letter" key="B_1718-01-01_991170514608405501">literas</rs> meas ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> cito transmi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sisti, tum et quidem pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue quia in <rs type="letter" key="B_1718-01-14_991170517037505501">epistola</rs> Tua hodie <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me
               <lb/>accepta certiorem me facere voluisti pro amicitia Tua de
               <lb/>sermonibus<del> de me</del> coram Patritiis quibusdam Excellentissimis de
               <pb facs="1038400" n="144r"/>
<lb/>me habitis. Nescio sane, qua in re occasionem dare potuerim
               <lb/>iniqui de me sparsi rumoris; vehementer itaque <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te scire
               <lb/>aveo, quales sint et in quibus consistant ist<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> querel<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> eo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum qui de me parum bene locuti sunt,<del> si tamen ist<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pro-</del>
<lb/><del>fi </del>ut si quid forte <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me peccatum fuerit id corrigam. Si ta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>men ist<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> querel<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> duntaxat proficiscantur ab inimicis nostris,
               <lb/>et ut suspicari fas est <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> scienti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Mathematic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ignaris,<del> est</del>
<lb/><del>quod me </del>erit quod me consoler. Omnibus enim placere
               <lb/>velle stultitia est. Ego jam mihi proposueram conscribere
               <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dam edenda proximis vacationibus, quod propositum
               <lb/>itaque accedente Tuo consilio exequar, ut iniquorum
               <lb/>ora occludantur. Rogo Te autem ut interim de hoc meo propo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sito ad neminem verba facias. <abbr>D.</abbr> Marchio <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Polenus</rs> heri <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Ve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>netias</rs> abivit secum ferens duo <rs type="biblios">scripta</rs><!-- bibliotag (2 Publikationen, die im Giornale de' Letterati d'Italia (Diario) erscheinen soll) --> mea Diario inserenda;
               <lb/>unum<!-- bibliotag --> concernit Problema olim <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me propositum, estque idem<!-- bibliotag -->
<lb/>quod olim Tibi miseram sub nomine <rs type="person">Patruelis</rs><!-- ToDo: Persontag (heruausfinden, ob es sich um Nic. II oder Dan. I handelt) --> mei edendum,
               <lb/>mutatis tamen quibusdam et paucis additis;<note type="internal">ToDo: Kommentierung hinzufügen.</note> alterum est obser<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vatio in Theorema quoddam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117498068">Fagnano</rs> in <abbr>Tom.</abbr> 27. Diarii
               <lb/>propositum. Habeo etiam paratam aliam animadversionem
               <lb/>in locum quendam <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtoni</rs> et <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Herma<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>i</rs>, quam alio tempore
               <lb/>edam. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> meas redditas fuisse <rs type="letter">literas</rs><!-- brieftag --> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person">fratre</rs><!-- ToDo: person --> audivi, sed
               <lb/>ipsum antequam mihi rescribat, Tuum expectare ad suas aliquas
   <lb/><rs type="letter">responsum</rs><!-- brieftag -->. Idem <rs type="person">frater</rs><!-- persontag --> meus mihi nuntiavit, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruelem</rs> meum
               <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs> redeuntem ultra mensem <rs key="place_GEO-2973783" type="place">Argentorati</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> morbo deten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum<del> esse</del> fuisse, sed mox <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> affuturum esse. Sub finem
               <lb/>Bacchanaliorum<note type="editorial">Der Karneval endete am Aschermittwoch, vlg. Rust, Sandra Maria, Venedig und der Karneval. In: Schallaburg Kulturbetriebsges.m.b.H. (Hrsg.), Venedig – Seemacht, Kunst und Karneval. Schallaburg Kulturbetriebsgesellschaft, Schallaburg 2011, p. 247.</note> forte ad Vos veniam.
            </p>
<closer>Interim fave et Vale.
               <lb/><dateline><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <date when="1718-01-30"><abbr>d.</abbr> 30. <abbr>Jan.</abbr> 1718</date>.</dateline>
</closer>
<postscript><p>Repeto gratiarum actionem pro optima
               <lb/>quam suscepisti mei defensionem.</p></postscript>
</div>
